Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:29.89,ef_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs64\fsp-2\fscx80\bord0.5\be1\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(350,373)}Šindó Kei
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:34.40,ef_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\fsp-1\fscx80\bord0.8\be1\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(365,71)}Doručená zpráva
